### **9. Conclusion**  
By reinvesting exit taxes into the bonding curveâ€™s reserve, PumpHodl v2 transforms short-term speculation into long-term price stability. This creates a flywheel effect where early volatility fuels sustainable growth, aligning incentives across all token holders.  

